data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! CORNER LOT, Must See!!! Don't wait to build!!!  WELCOME TO VISTA PALMS This home build in 2020 has been meticulously maintained, offering an open floor plan in a corner lot with easy access to the main entrance and walking distance to club house and amenities. Near to I75 US -301 for an effortless commute to MacDill AFB,Tampa, ST Pete and Bradenton. Less than an hour from Sarasota amazing beaches. Community includes LAWN CARE no need to be sweeting to keep a great landscape, also include fitness center, tennis court, pool, playground and walking trails making this a great feature to do activities with the family and save money. Call now to book your private tour!!
